Class HomeserverConnectionConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matrix.androidsdk.HomeserverConnectionConfig

      • HomeserverConnectionConfig

        public HomeserverConnectionConfig(android.net.Uri hsUri,
                                  android.net.Uri identityServerUri,
                                  Credentials credentials,
                                  ArrayList<Fingerprint> allowedFingerprints,
                                  boolean pin)
        Parameters:
        hsUri - The URI to use to connect to the homeserver
        identityServerUri - The URI to use to manage identity
        credentials - The credentials to use, if needed. Can be null.
        allowedFingerprints - If using SSL, allow server certs that match these fingerprints.
        pin - If true only allow certs matching given fingerprints, otherwise fallback to standard X509 checks.
